#

Garlic Yogurt Sauce

10 min
$2.5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Sauce

Tags:

SauceDipCondiment

Description

A creamy and tangy yogurt sauce infused with garlic, perfect for dipping or drizzling over your favorite dishes.

Ingredients

  • plain greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • fresh dill (optional): 1 teaspoon
